{"about_the_game":"&quot;Floating World&quot; is an ocean-themed survival building game where you must find food and resources to build a shelter and survive each day. Tame animals, build houses, craft tools\u2014your creativity and effort will guide you through this ocean world.<br>\ufeff<br>The game features numerous islands, a storyline, and puzzle elements, along with a wealth of building materials and tools. You can experiment with different architectural styles and use various tools to uncover the story of this floating world. \ud83c\udfdd\ufe0f\ud83d\udd0d\ud83d\udca1<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/biaoti.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br><br><strong>About the game</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build system</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/jianzhu.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83c\udfe0\ud83e\ude91 Building System: Expand your activity area on the sea with a building gun. Construct houses, roofs, and eaves to create a comfortable home. Decorate with a variety of furniture.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Navigation system</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/chuanfan.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83d\udee5\ufe0f\u2699\ufe0f Navigation System: Build sails for your raft. For faster travel, construct engines and rudders to better control your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">synth</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/hechegnqi.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83d\udd27\ud83d\udd29 Synthesizer: Almost everything in the floating world can be crafted with this machine. Resources can also be recycled using it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Backpack system</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/Game_backpack_VR~2.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83c\udf92\ud83c\udfae Backpack System: Designed for VR, the backpack system allows you to store items just like in real life. Quickly place items in your backpack or use the quick insert button.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Survival Farming System</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/zhongcai.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83c\udf31\ud83d\udc16 Survival Farming System: Besides basic ocean activities like fishing and grilling fish, you can also build planting pots to grow your own plants and even raise pigs on your raft.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different game modes</h2>\ud83c\udfae\ud83c\udfa8 Different Game Modes: The game offers Easy, Normal, Hard, Peaceful, and Creative modes. Creative mode allows you to freely build your creations without worrying about resource consumption.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/feixing.gif?t=1717724779\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/kaichuan.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br>\ud83d\udd28\ud83d\udd2e Item Upgrade System: In the later stages, build an upgrader, mining machine, and teleporter to enhance your ship and make exploring the world easier.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/xiaomifeng.gif?t=1717724779\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/extras/paizao.gif?t=1717724779\" /><br><i>More functions, looking forward to your try in the game :)</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1717724779","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2006050/page.bg.jpg?t=1717724779","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as